Gateway to Bell's Toll~
Before you towers an arching gateway.  The pillars seem to be composed of
bone and the arch above the gates is lined with ancient skulls.  The eerie
stillness of the forest pervades here, yet you have the feeling of being
watched.  A sudden gust of wind from the west brings the stench of death,
and to your east, the turrets of Castle Bloodbane rise to the sky.  Above
the grinning skulls is a rotted wooden sign, proclaiming this the entrance
to Bell's Toll.  You can enter Bell's Toll to the north, or leave this place
to the south.
~
